videos.title: The Greatest Moments in Magic Streaming History
videos.description:
Today we're looking at the most viewed Twitch clips in Magic: the Gathering history, giving us a look at some of the game's most iconic, funniest and weirdest moments all in 60 seconds or less! Let's give them a watch!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
